      "instruction": "<p>Deseed the<strong> red pepper<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and chop into large bite-sized pieces</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
