            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a full kettle</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>meat-free chicken</strong> and cook for 3 min or until starting to brown</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
