    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once golden, add the<strong> chopped pepper </strong>to the pan with the meat-free chicken</p><p>Add the <strong>ginger paste</strong> and <strong>garlic</strong> and cook for 4-5 min further or until the pepper is beginning to soften</p>",
